title: Night.Of.The.Living.Dead.1968.DvDRip.Xvid.Swesub-Dark_Lord.avi
description: Terror reigns. Panic and paranoia take their toll. No one knows why the dead are returning to life, only that the living are their eviscerated victims. In a remote wooden farmhouse seven people fight for their lives against ever-increasing numbers of flesh-eating ghouls. One by one they are whittled down until, in a memorable shock finale, only a lone hero remains, cowering in the cellar while legions of ravenous zombies run amok. As the sun rises, he emereges into a new dawn... has he survived the Night of the living dead?
